In order to prepare the different BDT you will first need to prepare the Data used in the training.

For that you need to use the line : 
python3 prepare_samples.py config_preparation_DplusToPiKPi.yml

After that you can do the training with : 
python3 ML_Training.py training_config_DplusToPiKPi.yml

If you want to a preselection different for the differents Pt bins you will need to train several BDT, one for each Pt bin.
Be carefull to save the BDT model in different folder if you do that, or you will erase the last one.